{"tid":1928254,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港寬頻再派糖：送經濟困難家庭 兩年免費寬頻 名額1萬個","createTime":"2020-03-16T09:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T09:32:44.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"56d9b1fb1352ff0776134b518f0054e0aeb96d07","tid":1928254,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T09:30:09.000Z","msg":"香港寬頻（1310）繼早前豁免住宅及企業客戶一個月服務月費後，最新公佈向1萬名有經濟困難人士及家庭，送出兩年免費住宅寬頻服務。<br />\n<br />\n公告指，現時香港大多數學校處於停課期間，學校轉而透過網上教學，讓學生能夠停課不停學。然而，由於經濟困難等因素，並非所有人均能享受高速寬頻服務，因此公司提供免費寬頻以紓緩基層的財政壓力。<br />\n<br />\n今次的免費計劃包括100Mbps寬頻、Wi-Fi 管家（即路由器）及myTV SUPER 基本版服務，豁免安裝費，申請人另可選擇以優惠價每月HK$10同時享用家居電話及IDD 0030（包每月30分鐘免費通話）服務。<br />\n<br />\n免費寬頻申請日期由今年4月1日起至8月31日，有經濟困難的人士及家庭，無論是否現有香港寬頻住宅客戶，均可經以下七家合作機構申請此計劃，包括明愛青少年及社區服務、教會關懷貧窮網絡、香港家庭福利會、香港基督教女青年會、聖雅各福群會、香港學校訓輔人員協會及香港復康會。合作機構將負責核實申請人是否符合申請資格。有關計劃詳情及合作機構聯絡方法，可瀏覽<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200316/QZBJBB3XNYPEUZY4BN2K7UNSHU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200316%2FQZBJBB3XNYPEUZY4BN2K7UNSHU%2F&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebSbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=6f07ebdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200316%2FQZBJBB3XNYPEUZY4BN2K7UNSHU%2F&h=cd758c5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200316/QZBJBB3XNYPEUZY4BN2K7UNSHU/</a>"},{"pid":"4d43b696278410d44b45f697bda9d5513f7f0ab3","tid":1928254,"uid":3028,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T09:31:06.000Z","msg":"100mb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如56k啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1804b66077f5e4f08388703bdcc025d601896869","tid":1928254,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d43b696278410d44b45f697bda9d5513f7f0ab3","tid":1928254,"uid":3028,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T09:31:06.000Z","msg":"100mb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如56k啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T09:32:44.000Z","msg":"我唐樓得6MB定8MB咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}